Rmd b63ea9b daiuc 2022-08-01 wflow_publish("leafcutterMD_20220801.Rmd")

GTEx Muscle

group0

Intron selection

Introns must satisfy the following criteria, based on p_cutoff = 1e-08

  1. cluster level p-value < 1e-08
  2. minimum p-value of a given intron < 1e-08

Introns that have outlier splicing events: Based on the above criteria, 24813 intron clusters, and 25665 outlier introns are selected. Below are the outlier introns (top 500 rows):

intron[cluster %in% outlier_clusters & 
            rowMins < p_cutoff
          ][order(rowMins)] %>% head(500)

QQ plot

Select top 4 introns and plot qq plot:

intron[
  cluster %in% outlier_clusters & rowMins < p_cutoff][
    order(rowMins)] %>% 
  head(4) %>% 
  .[, -c("cluster", "rowMins")] %>% 
  column_to_rownames("chrom") %>% t %>% as.data.frame %>% as.list %>% 
  leafcutter::multiqq(.) + theme_bw() + 
    guides(color = guide_legend(nrow=2, title=NULL)) + 
    theme(legend.position = "bottom")

QQ plot of introns with outlier splicing

Box plot of selected introns

Histgram of number of detected outlier samples per intron

Outlier Summary

Overall in GTEX Muscle group0 with pvalue cutoff at 10^{-8}, there are in total 25665 outlier introns detected, that occurred among 100 samples
